{"title":"Git常用命令","date":"2019-06-21T09:45:27.000Z","slug":"other-git","tags":["git"],"categories":["Others"],"updated":"2019-06-21T10:08:22.000Z","content":"<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git init //初始化git仓库</span><br><span class=\"line\">git add [文件...] //添加到仓库</span><br><span class=\"line\">git commit [文件...] -m &quot;注释&quot; //提交一个版本</span><br><span class=\"line\">git status //查看状态</span><br><span class=\"line\">git diff [文件] //查看变更</span><br><span class=\"line\">git diff HEAD -- readme.txt //查看某个版本中的文件与当前文件的不同</span><br><span class=\"line\">git log [--pretty=oneline] //查看提交记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">git reset --hard HEAD //重置到当前版本</span><br><span class=\"line\">git reset --hard HEAD^ //重置到上一个版本</span><br><span class=\"line\">git reset --hard HEAD^^ //重置到上上一个版本</span><br><span class=\"line\">git reset --hard HEAD~100 //重置到第前100个版本</span><br><span class=\"line\">git reset --hard 1094a //重置到版本id为1094a开头的那个版本</span><br><span class=\"line\">git reflog //查看操作记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">git checkout -- readme.txt //丢弃工作区的更改</span><br><span class=\"line\">git reset HEAD readme.txt //丢弃暂存区的修改（从某一个版本中的某个文件覆盖）</span><br><span class=\"line\">git rm test.txt //从版本库中删除文件 需要commit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"说明\">说明<a href=\"post/other-git#说明\"></a></h2><p>上面内容全部来自<a href=\"https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/wiki/896043488029600\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">廖雪峰 Git教程</a>，为了阅读方便放到了这里。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"归并排序、快速排序","slug":"algorithm-sort"},"next":{"title":"VSCode 扩展开发(十) TreeView","slug":"vscode-ext10"},"link":"http://lilpig.site/post/other-git/","toc":[{"title":"说明","id":"说明","index":"1"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"LIL PIG","link":"<a href=\"http://lilpig.site/post/other-git/\" title=\"Git常用命令\">http://lilpig.site/post/other-git/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}